lead_paragraph: Germany midfielder Toni Kroos will miss the World Cup qualifier against San Marino on Friday after fracturing a bone in his right foot during Real Madrid's league game against Leganes on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Germany Midfielder Kroos to Miss San Marino Qualifier
